    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1957-05-30T10:06:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1957-05-30T10:06:00-05:00" n="211"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d211">
                <head>211. Telegram From the <gloss type="from">Department of State</gloss> to the
                        <gloss type="to">Embassy in the United Kindom</gloss>
                    <note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d211fn1">Source: Department of State, Central
                        Files, 330.13/5–3057. Secret; Priority.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1957-05-30T11:06:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 30, 1957—11:06 a.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>8377. For <persName corresp="#p_SHE1">Stassen</persName> From Acting Secretary. I
                    trust we shall receive promptly the revised basic paper incorporating May 25
                    decisions which you discussed with Secretary on Sunday.<note n="2"
                        xml:id="d211fn2">See <ref target="#d206">Documents 206</ref> and <ref
                            target="#d207">207</ref>.</note> President expects this to be agreed by
                    interested agencies here and then submitted to him before you undertake detailed
                    negotiations based on the revised policy.<note n="3" xml:id="d211fn3">
                        <ref target="#d212">
                            <hi rend="italic">Infra</hi>
                        </ref>.</note>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_HCA1">
                            <hi rend="strong">Herter</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
